Introduction

Two X was a four-member girl group under Star Gaze Entertainment. They originally debuted under J.Tune Camp as five on August 16, 2012, with the single album "Double Up".

In January 2016, it was announced that Minjoo had left the group.

In June 2018, Eun revealed via Instagram that the group had disbanded quietly.
